  "text": "We developed a phrase based sentiment detection system geared towards Social Media by augmenting the state of the art system developed by [CITATION_1] to include additional dictionaries such as Wiktionary and new features such as word lengthening (e.g. helllllloooo) and emoticons (e.g. :)) [CITATION_2] . We initially evaluated our system through our participation in the first Sentiment Analysis in Twitter task [CITATION_3] . We have improved our system this year by adding a new dictionary and additional features.",
